data.description: -----OPEN HOUSE IS CANCELLED-----  WELCOME to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath colonial in the sought after Old Stage Knolls community.  LOW HOA! One-Year HOME WARRANTY included! As you enter the property you are greeted by a beautiful open foyer and balcony stairs. To your right, you will find a home office with French doors and updated powder room.  On your left is an open concept formal living room that flows directly into your formal dining room with bay window and molding trim work.  As you enter the kitchen, you will notice the open concept to the great/family room. Kitchen features include an appealing island, desirable eat-in dining area with upgraded granite countertops, wood cabinets, and pantry.  Step down and unwind in the sizable family room with plenty of natural light, a brick fireplace, and vaulted ceilings - perfect for entertaining. Walk outside to the rear to find the large deck, overlooking the expansive, privately fenced backyard - backed to the trees/wood! The upper level features a lovely spacious primary suite with an impressively sized walk-in closet and ensuite bath featuring dual vanities, separate shower, and a large spa-like sunken tub.  Enjoy three additional bedrooms and another full bath! The lower level is an open canvas for whatever you may desire. Bathroom rough-in is awaiting another bathroom install.  This beauty also includes access to the 2-car garage and a driveway large enough for 2+ cars.  Conveniently located near commuter routes including Route 50, 450 and 197, parks and plenty of walking trails. Just 15 minutes from DC & Annapolis and 25 minutes from Fort Meade & Joint Base Andrews. Lots of amenities just minutes away including the Baysox Stadium, Bowie Town Center, grocery stores, urgent care centers, gas stations, tons of shopping & dining choices… and so much more!! Schedule your showing today.
